reviewText: the best of kim rae won, next is 'what star are you from' where he's ruggedly handsome, these are the must see dramas of rae won. kim tae hee is pretty on screen, i love the chemistry of these two performers. just be careful in selecting a seller of this drama, i had a bad experience buying this drama because the 3rd disc wouldn't play, i sent it back to the seller for replacement & i got the same broken disc back.
I loved this movie.  It is a great love story and the characters who are in love with each other are together more than not.
